1
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,280
If you are sleepy,

2
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,440
rest early.

3
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:03,120
I am a disaster to the nation right now.

4
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,560
Since you haven't slept,

5
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,560
how dare I sleep?

6
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,960
Eunuch Jingyuan.

7
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,970
You must not lose your manners.

8
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:12,640
Your Majesty.

9
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:15,400
The little prince was framed for adultery with Consort Rong.

10
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,760
The Eldest Princess just sent people to catch them.

11
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,960
Now the little prince

12
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,860
has been forcibly taken away.

13
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,930
What did you say?

14
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,760
The Eldest Princess clearly lives outside the palace.

15
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,520
But she came in the middle of the night

16
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,039
to catch adulterers.

17
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,420
I am afraid this

18
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,880
is targeted at me.

19
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:35,560
The one about to be executed

20
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:38,700
is Your Majesty's most beloved brother.

21
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:40,759
Summon

22
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,560
Si Xinglan immediately.

23
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:45,320
Why did Your Majesty summon me?

24
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:00,400
I would like to ask Her Highness the Grand Princess.

25
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,080
What did you do to Ayan?

26
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:08,560
Si Xingyan had an affair with His Majesty's Consort Rong.

27
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,240
He defiled the inner palace,

28
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,640
and lost all decency.

29
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,640
I am His Majesty's aunt.

30
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:18,000
Naturally, I must consider his reputation.

31
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:21,640
So I must deal with Si Xingyan properly.

32
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,280
Ayan is simple-minded.

33
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:28,280
I fear someone framed him.

34
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,440
Framed?

35
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:32,360
He is a prince.

36
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,200
If His Majesty didn't give the order,

37
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,600
who would dare touch him?

38
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,320
According to the ancestral system,

39
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:41,600
royal family members must go to their fiefs upon coming of age.

40
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:44,079
Yet Ayan has always stayed in the palace,

41
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:45,720
which is certainly against the rules.

42
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:47,800
Now that such a thing has happened,

43
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:50,800
I think it's time to send him away.

44
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,680
Is that so?

45
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,500
To me, it looks like

46
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,480
you want Ayan's life.

47
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,880
Hahaha.

48
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,160
Anyway,

49
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:04,520
I am the biological aunt of Your Majesty and Ayan.

50
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,920
If not for your sake,

51
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,480
I wouldn't have brought this up.

52
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,240
Ayan only has the mind of a seven-year-old.

53
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,800
If you make him go to his fief,

54
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,600
you are sending him to his death.

55
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,840
Even if he lacks intelligence,

56
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,600
he is an adult man.

57
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,160
His illness is in his brain,

58
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,760
not his body.

59
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:29,440
You must never treat him as a child.

60
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,240
It seems, Aunt,

61
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,370
you are determined to force me.

62
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,720
This matter is of great importance.

63
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,560
Forgive me, but I cannot yield.

64
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:54,040
If Your Majesty insists on protecting Si Xingyan,

65
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:56,280
then I will summon the ministers,

66
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:59,640
and let the whole court judge carefully

67
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,440
who is right and who is wrong.

68
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,680
Your Majesty.

69
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:14,280
Both the Grand Princess and Consort Rong are suspects.

70
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,480
I hope Your Majesty

71
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,970
will investigate thoroughly.

72
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:27,100
How dare you block the Grand Princess's way!

73
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,360
Do you have a death wish?

74
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,720
Then can I block it?

75
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,720
What are you doing, Your Majesty?

76
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,720
Didn't you want to punish A'yan severely, Aunt?

77
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,640
If so,

78
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,240
why not hand over Consort Rong and A'yan

79
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,040
so I can convict them?

80
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,640
Consort Rong and A'yan have committed a grave crime,

81
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,760
and I have already arrested them.

82
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:03,360
I'm afraid it's inconvenient for Your Majesty to personally try such a trivial matter.

83
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:06,320
Aunt, if you refuse to hand over Consort Rong and A'yan,

84
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,920
think I'm blind,

85
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,080
and convict them yourself,

86
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:12,480
don't blame me for suspecting you of plotting to murder A'yan

87
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,440
and committing treason.

88
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:23,160
What are you talking about, Your Majesty?

89
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,520
If this matter blows up,

90
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,080
it will damage the royal family's reputation.

91
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,960
Therefore, I wanted to keep it quiet

92
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,640
and arrest the person myself.

93
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,680
If Your Majesty doesn't care about your reputation,

94
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:35,240
I will simply hand the person over.

95
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:40,370
Handing the person over so easily,

96
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,370
there must be something fishy.

97
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,840
Your Majesty is close to Ayan.

98
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,200
I naturally understand.

99
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,800
And exactly because of this,

100
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,840
I fear Your Majesty might protect Ayan

101
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,700
and damage the royal reputation.

102
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,440
How about this?

103
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,840
You can take Consort Rong back for interrogation first.

104
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,560
If her words are false,

105
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:07,280
it won't be too late for me to hand Ayan over.

106
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,400
What?

107
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:15,160
Does Your Majesty not want to interrogate?

108
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:16,800
Guards!

109
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,780
Go fetch Consort Rong.

110
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:21,400
I will personally interrogate her thoroughly.

111
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:21,880
Yes.

112
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,720
Trying to start with Consort Rong?

113
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,280
Si Xingxuan,

114
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,880
you are just wasting your effort.

115
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,800
I truly love the young prince.

116
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,280
Please grant my request, Your Majesty.

117
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,640
I know you are lying.

118
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,560
As long as you tell the truth,

119
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,580
His Majesty

120
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:43,159
will have someone send you out of the palace.

121
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:43,800
Really?

122
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,120
I am the Emperor.

123
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,560
I keep my word.

124
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,240
I don't need to leave the palace.

125
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,480
I don't need to leave the palace.

126
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,840
As long as you can save my sister,

127
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,280
I will tell you the truth.

128
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,880
Where is your sister now?

129
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,080
I don't know.

130
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,760
I only know

131
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,540
they relocate at any time.

132
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,760
Before this,

133
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:05,290
she had been in the Grand Princess's mansion.

134
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,320
As long as you are willing to testify,

135
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:09,240
I will send someone to find her right now

136
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,500
and ensure her safety.

137
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,640
Unless I see my sister,

138
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,440
I won't tell you anything.

139
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,240
Given my aunt's methods,

140
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:20,040
she will definitely impeach Yan tomorrow morning.

141
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,240
If we can't find it tonight,

142
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,840
there won't be a tomorrow.

143
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,900
I'll go stall for time.

144
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,240
Your Highness.

145
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,240
His Majesty didn't find out anything yesterday.

146
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,840
The ministers have signed,

147
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:40,370
willing to jointly impeach the young prince.

148
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:49,440
Are you going to the palace, Your Highness?

149
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:53,520
Before His Majesty uncovers the truth,

150
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:57,890
I must present the ministers' joint impeachment memorial.

151
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,560
This way,

152
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:03,560
the initiative will still be in my hands.

153
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,300
Are we really going to impeach that fool?

154
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,770
If His Majesty wants to make a move against me,

155
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,920
I will make a move against Si Xingyan.

156
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,520
If he knows what's good for him,

157
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:18,040
and comes to me now to beg for mercy and apologize,

158
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:21,040
I might still forgive him.

159
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,440
Your Highness, someone is asking to see you.

160
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,240
Yes.

161
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:26,920
It seems His Majesty knows what's good for him.

162
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,880
Let him in.

163
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,960
Jing Yuan of Yuqing Palace pays respects to the Grand Princess.

164
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,120
A eunuch.

165
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,320
Is there no one left by His Majesty's side?

166
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,960
I am not here for His Majesty.

167
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,760
I am here for the little prince.

168
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,160
The little prince is kind-hearted.

169
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,420
Please spare his life.

170
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:55,880
I have seen Your Highness treat the little prince with kindness,

171
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:58,840
and surely you wouldn't bear to see him sent to the frontier to die in vain.

172
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,280
Please reconsider, Your Highness.

173
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,040
Why do you say that?

174
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:05,640
I love A'yan very much.

175
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,920
But,

176
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:09,560
he made a mistake a man shouldn't make.

177
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,080
He fell in love with the Emperor's woman.

178
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,520
I cannot forgive him.

179
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,080
Bring the memorial.

180
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,690
Your Highness. Your Highness.

181
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,840
Your Highness.
